Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/storybot.git

Open CMD and type:
cd storybot #folder name

Create a virtual environment (optional but recommended):
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate  # On Windows

Install dependencies:
pip install openai

Don't forget to add your secret API key in the code:
Add your OpenAI API key in the code where indicated.
